[3.386311, "o", "Go-K8SDeploy - Pipeline deterministico: validate -> build -> apply -> health-check -> rollback (License Token: VGhpcyBwcm9kdWN0IGlzIGRldmVsb3BlZCBieSBZb3VyIE5ldCBUZWMuIExpY2Vuc2U6IEFHUEwu)\r\n\r\n"]
[3.387716, "o", "Usage:\r\n  go-k8sdeploy [command]\r\n\r\nAvailable Commands:\r\n  apply       Executa deploy completo deterministico"]
[3.388616, "o", "\r\n  appset      Gera apps a partir de templates (Application Sets)\r\n  bench       Benchmark suite (latencia + throughput do sistema)\r\n  completion  Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell\r\n  daemon      Auto-sync ao detectar mudancas em manifests\r\n  drift       Detecta drift entre cluster e manifestos\r\n  help        Help about any command\r\n  init        Inicializa estrutura do projeto\r\n  logs        Logs do deploy\r\n  notify      Envia notificacao manual\r\n  plan        Mostra plano de execucao (dry-run)\r\n  rbac        Gerenciamento de RBAC\r\n  rollback    Reverte para revisao\r\n  rollout     Progressive delivery (canary, blue/green, A/B)\r\n  status      Status do deploy atual\r\n  web         Inicia UI Dashboard web (porta 8585)\r\n  webhook     Inicia receptor de webhooks GitOps (GitHub/GitLab)\r\n\r\nFlags:\r\n  -h, --help              help for go-k8sdeploy\r\n  -p, --project string    Nome do projeto\r\n      --work-dir string   Diretorio de trabalho (default \"/opt/k8s-deploy\")\r\n\r\nUse \"go-k8sdeploy [command] --help\" for more information about a command.\r\n"]
[3.390821, "o", "\r\n"]
